# Schematics

Schematics are files containing block and entity information of a certain area a player scanned with the {% item name="structurize/scan_tool" /%} in-game. You can use the {% item name="structurize/scan_tool" /%} and scan ANY building or structure you like in singleplayer or multiplayer and then have your {% worker name="builder" /%} build it for you (provided that you give them all the materials needed, of course).

